#. Tag: title
#: introduction.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:3
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kapp; is a program that lets you create cross stitch patterns and "
#| "charts. Patterns can be created from scratch on a user defined size of "
#| "grid, which can be enlarged or reduced in size as your pattern "
#| "progresses. Alternatively you can import images from many graphics "
#| "formats. When importing images you can restrict the conversion to full "
#| "stitches or optionally use fractional stitches. You may also use images "
#| "as backgrounds resizing them to fit in a selected area. These imported "
#| "images can then be modified using the supplied tools to produce your "
#| "final design."
msgid ""
"&kxstitch; is a program that lets you create cross stitch patterns and "
"charts. Patterns can be created from scratch on a user defined size of grid, "
"which can be enlarged or reduced in size as your pattern progresses. "
"Alternatively you can import images from many graphics formats. When "
"importing images you can restrict the conversion to full stitches or "
"optionally use fractional stitches. You may also use images as backgrounds "
"resizing them to fit in a selected area. These imported images can then be "
"modified using the supplied tools to produce your final design."
msgstr ""
"&kapp; je program koji vam omogućava da kreirate uzorke za goblene i "
"grafikone. Uzorci mogu biti kreirani od nule na korisnički definisanoj "
"veličini mreže, koja se može uvećati ili smanjiti kako vaš obrazac "
"napreduje. Alternativno možete da uvezete slike iz mnogih grafičkih formata. "
"Kod prebacivanje slika možete ograničiti konverziju do punog uboda ili "
"eventualno korišćenje djelomičnih šavova. Takođe možete koristiti slike kao "
"pozadina mijenjajući im veličinu da stane u izabranoj oblasti. Ove uvezene "
"slike  se zatim mogu modifikovati pomoću priloženog alata za proizvodnju "
"vašegj finalnog dizajna."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are many tools to aid designing your pattern, from open and filled "
"rectangles and ellipses, filled polygons and lines and backstitching. "
"Additionally cut, copy and paste can be used to duplicate selected areas. "
"Selected areas can also be rotated 90, 180 and 270 degrees anti clockwise, "
"or mirrored horizontally or vertically."
msgstr ""
"Mnogo je opcija koje mogu pomoci tvom paternu, od otvaranja i popunjavanja "
"pravouganika i elipsi, popunjavanja poligona i linija kao i pravljenje "
"duplih šavova. Dodatno \"izrezi\", \"kopiraj\" i \"zalijepi\" moze biti "
"iskoristeno da duplicira označena područja. Označena područja isto tako mogu "
"biti zarotirana 90, 180 i 270 stepeni obrnuto od smjera kazaljke na satu, "
"ili ogledano horizontalno ili vertikalno."

#. Tag: para
#: introduction.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also a pattern library that can be used to store small and not so "
"small portions of patterns that can then be reused in other patterns. The "
"patterns in these libraries are stored in a hierarchical list that makes it "
"easy to sort and navigate them to find the ones you want. These pattern "
"libraries can also be used as alphabets by assigning a character to each "
"one. By using the Alphabet tool, each key press is searched for in the "
"current library and if present, the associated library pattern will be "
"inserted in the pattern."
msgstr ""
"Tu je i biblioteka uzoraka koja se može koristiti za spremanje malih i ne "
"tako malih dijelova uzorka koje se onda mogu ponovno koristiti za druge "
"uzorke. Uzorci u ovim bibliotekama se čuvaju u hijerarhijskoj listi koja "
"olakšava sortiranje i navigaciju da pronađete one koje želite. Ove obrazac "
"biblioteke se također mogu koristiti kao alfabeti dodjeljujući znak svakoj. "
"Korištenjem Alfabet alata, svaki pritisak na taster se traži u tekućoj "
"biblioteci i ako je prisutan, pridružena biblioteka obrazaca će biti ubačena "
"u obrazac."

